  "article": "In a groundbreaking development, the renowned Wolfram technology is rapidly emerging as an essential foundation for the next generation of large language model (LLM) systems. As the AI industry continues to push the boundaries of what's possible, the integration of Wolfram's powerful computational capabilities is poised to revolutionize the way these advanced models are developed and deployed.

